<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆想要做新的皇家魔法师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人也都想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但只有一个魔法师可以参加选拔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会很快选出最好的魔法师。”魔法老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆练习了很多魔法咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他魔法师也是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，老师找来了所有的魔法师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每个人必须变出一个礼物来。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会选出最好的礼物，还有最好的魔法师。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瓦尔特大笑道：“汤姆是变不出礼物的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他魔法师也大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>魔法师们变出了好吃的蛋糕和糖果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有金币和笔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆举起了他的魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会给每个人一双有点点花纹的红袜子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！“你这个傻瓜！”瓦尔特大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你让我们长了红点点！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在都得了水痘啦！”另一个魔法师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“除了你以外，每个人都生病了，汤姆。”老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只能你去皇宫了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会尽力的，老师！”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆准备好了行李，很快就出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，他又回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老师？”汤姆问，“皇宫在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老师叹了口气，给了汤姆一张地图。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你要走过黑暗森林。”老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一路上会很危险。你一定要照着地图走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆拿着地图向着黑暗森林走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>